TRS-AI (bootable BASIC appliance integration)
Copyright (c) 2026 Charles Benedict Jr

This repository ships mkosi recipes, shell/Python tooling, and documentation
that build a Fedora guest image containing MBASIC.

The interpreter and compiler sources live in the mbasic/ directory, which is
a git submodule:

  https://github.com/chuckb/mbasic

That project is a fork of:

  https://github.com/avwohl/mbasic

